super yummy! i agree with the other reviews...cut down the water a bit and add more sour cream (only a quarter cup extra in my opinion, but if you love sour cream go for a little bit more). also....make this dish early and let it sit for a while, the flavor triples! i brought this dish to a thanksgiving party and found out later that other people where taking credit for it! absolute comfort food gold!

