Rating: 1
I had a bad feeling about this recipe - way too much water! After cooking, the leeks completely disintegrate into the overly watered potatoes. The end result shows - complete lack of richness or real taste - only a watery flavor, and that's with reducing the amount of liquid. This recipe would be improved dramatically if the potatoes were cooked separately from the leeks and they were combined at the end.

Rating: 3
